title: Cozy Roseville 1 bedroom

posting_body: ['PLEASE NOTE:', 'For more information on this listing please call', 'show contact info', 'and leave a voice message.', ' We do NOT respond to text messages or email.', 'Thank you!', 'About the location:', 'Available August 1st!', ' This cozy one bedroom, one bath apartment is in a quiet building with great neighbors.', 'This unit features solid-wood flooring throughout with an open layout and plentiful closet / storage space including a large entry way closet, linen closet, large bedroom closet, (downstairs storage locker also available for a small fee).', 'There is also on-site laundry and off-street parking behind the building.', 'The building is located just a few blocks away from the bus line as well as highways 35 and 36.', 'There are also a plethora of shopping within a less than two miles including Rosedale Mall, HarMar, Target, and Cub Foods.', 'If you are looking for outdoor recreation we have that too!', 'Our building is walking distance from Lake Josephine, Como Lake, the Como Zoo, and several other area parks.', 'The best way to get ahold of us is to call', 'show contact info', ', and answer the following questions.', '(We do not respond to texts.)', 'Thanks!', 'When calling please leave the following information:', "1) what month you'd like to move-in", '2) how many people will be in the unit', '3) any pets, how many and what kind.', 'If it is a dog please include the size and breed.', '4) whether you are working full or part time, and if you are receiving any additional government assistance etc.', '5) if you or any of your roommates have any evictions or unlawful detainers', '6) if you or your roommates have a  criminal background', '7) if you have rental history', 'To set up a showing please call', 'show contact info', 'and leave a message mentioning "Lexington Avenue 1-bedroom" We do not respond to text messages; please call!', 'Rental Criteria :', '- Credit and background check required.', '- Rental references from landlord/management required.', '- Proof of income required.', '- Non', '-smoking.', 'Pets are welcome with pet deposit and monthly pet charge in addition to listed monthly rent.', '-Small dogs are welcome ( 25lbs or less )', '-Cats must be spayed/neutered', 'The rent is $895 per month plus utilities.', 'To set up a showing please call', 'show contact info', ', and leave a message mentioning "Lexington Avenue 1-bedroom".', 'We do not respond to text messages;
